## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-186">属性的大多数<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities>，具有"功能"末尾的名称，如<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>，是枚举类型的值的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-186">Most of the properties of <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities> that have "Capability" at the end of the name, such as <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.CollationCapability%2A>, are collections of values of an enumerated type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-187">但是<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>和<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A>是对象的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-187">But <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A> and <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageResolutionCapability%2A> are collections of objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-188">对于后一种的两个属性，不能通过使用测试是否存在特定值**Contains**方法<xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-188">For the latter two properties, you cannot test for the presence of a particular value by using the **Contains** method of <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-189">这是因为对于引用类型，该方法返回`true`仅当对象的内存地址传递给它与集合中对象的地址相同; 即，它们是相同的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-189">This is because, with reference types, the method returns `true` only when the memory address of the object passed to it is the same as the address of an object in the collection; that is, they are the same object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-190">这将不通常会出现这种情况，该方法将几乎始终返回`false`即使没有对象具有完全相同值的所有属性的集合中对象传递给**Contains**方法 <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-190">Since this will not usually be the case, the method will nearly always return `false` even if there is an object in the collection with exactly the same values in all its properties as the object passed to the **Contains** method of  <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-191">若要确定的内容<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>，你必须枚举其每个成员，与所需的值进行比较。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-191">To determine the contents of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>, you must enumerate through each of its members, comparing them with the desired value.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-192">如果打印机不支持媒体大小选择，该集合为空。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-192">If the printer does not support media size selection, the collection is empty.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-193">此属性对应于[打印架构](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)的`PageMediaSize`关键字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-193">This property corresponds to the [Print Schema](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=186397)'s `PageMediaSize` keyword.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="07bd0-194">下面的代码示例演示如何搜索中的特定值<xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="07bd0-194">The following code example shows how to search for a particular value in the <xref:System.Printing.PrintCapabilities.PageMediaSizeCapability%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
foreach (PageMediaSize mediaSize in pc.PageMediaSizeCapability)  
    {  
        if (mediaSize.PageMediaSizeName == PageMediaSizeName.ISOA4)  
        {  
            Console.WriteLine("A4 size is supported");  
            break;  
        }  
    }  
```

  
  
